Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The universe,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}stretching out without bound...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}It is a an epic poem{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}of miracles and eternity,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}woven by the chains of life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Each of the countless lives that fill{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the galaxy are not of themselves eternal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}For all living things, life is{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}something that you only get one of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}It's how you have lived, and who{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}you have passed your dreams down to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Jose... Silver... Schneider...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Murase...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.40,0:01:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Guys, we managed to protect it! We...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, we protected Destiny,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and the Galaxy Railways.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've identified giant spatial distortions\N{\c&He1e1e1&}1000 spacekilos behind the combat zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're dimension holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You... Why are you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People inherit the{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}irreplaceable hopes of others,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}as they risk their{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}own irreplaceable lives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Far-Reaching Hope"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}New craft confirmed.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Enemy ships numbering around 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's a forced signal coming in\N{\c&He1e1e1&}on all communications circuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My name is Foresis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I will say this once. Renounce your\N{\c&He1e1e1&}control over Planet Destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and surrender your\N{\c&He1e1e1&}home station to us at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I will not say it again.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}This is your final notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've all performed well up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, I am not leaving {\i1}Big One.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}don't keep us at a distance.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}If you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}we won't be able to face\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the folks of Vega Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Everyone listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We are the Space Defense Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There is no way we can hand over\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the Galaxy Railways to the invaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We, along with {\i1}Big One,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}are going to overcome this crisis\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with all of our strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and protect the Galaxy Railways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Entrust me with your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Magnetic barrier output normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Boiler pressure normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Foresis-sama, sure enough, they\N{\c&He1e1e1&}have analyzed the Cosmo Matrix.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please cease your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}At this rate, we are going to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}suffer serious casualties as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Foresis-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Be silent, Treele.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}B- but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why do you defy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am disappointed in you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and your sister, you worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I do not need you to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Take her to mental reconstruction.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Crush the piece of lint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The giant battleship\N{\c&He1e1e1&}has increased speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Drawing to within 800 spacekilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, let's withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Against something that huge, I don't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}think random fire is going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's buy some time, find its\N{\c&He1e1e1&}weak point, and then attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We won't destroy it,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}but we will stop it in its tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and then negotiate again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}you think so? I guess\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that is the only way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, begin searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger! {\i1}Big One{\i0} changing course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the core...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain... David... Yuki... {\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} has altered course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}you saved us, Manabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Akatsuki-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}As it happens, we've got\N{\c&He1e1e1&}kind of a problem here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The makeshift bypass device got\N{\c&He1e1e1&}blown out in that last all-out attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Then we can't fire right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll make sure it's fixed... in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Akatsuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't have enough capacity\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to analyze the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The search subject is too large.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Akatsuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm all right. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Old-timer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Akatsuki-san,{\i0} instructions, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Such an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Prepare to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Utilize all systems to search for\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the giant battleship's weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry and come up\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with a firing solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Captain Julia!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Captain Julia!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Captain Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Looks like we're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Connect the blue cable directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't forget the pulse cycle\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for the encoder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Avoid damage to the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}main guns at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Identified the giant battleship's main\N{\c&He1e1e1&}power source, and five backup systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Three large-scale propulsion devices,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and two auxiliary systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Projecting areas believed\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to be crew quarter areas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}which will not be targets of our attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The red blinking areas\N{\c&He1e1e1&}are the energy control systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If we can target these effectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}we can halt their attack without\N{\c&He1e1e1&}actually destroying the whole battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Calculate the optimum attack points\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and firing sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Transmit the data to {\i1}Big One{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do you know the location\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of their command center?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're unable to search them.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}They've discovered us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It looks like they've raised a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That was pretty skillful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Akatsuki-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Unfortunately, this is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the best that we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How long can we fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}One shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bring {\i1}Big One{\i0} around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The small enemy craft\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is coming toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Miserable flea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where do we aim our one shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll have to aim for their\N{\c&He1e1e1&}heart at point-blank range.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Either wallop them, or be invaded, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Receiving position of the power core,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and firing trajectory data!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's coming from the giant battleship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One,{\i0} can you hear me?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Louis Fort Drake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Louis!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Image coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll explain later.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please accept this data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the command center\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of the giant battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I believe the commander\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's all I can do on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Can you come aboard,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and attempt direct negotiations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I was trained how to do\N{\c&He1e1e1&}searches in Spica Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you safe there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Change of strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Um, how is {\i1}Yuuki-kun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, I've carried {\i1}Akatsuki-san{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to the medical car. See to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun,{\i0} I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Enemy fighters approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're going to commence the final defensive\N{\c&He1e1e1&}action of the Galaxy Railways now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ready the Space Eagles for launch!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Prepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Treele!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Treele...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why didn't you escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I want to put a stop to this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Like I told you, we can't go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why not? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why does everyone have to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}spill their blood like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}so many of your comrades have died!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Even Leafle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no way your heart\N{\c&He1e1e1&}can't be aching, Treele!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}After all, you are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle's older sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Copy!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- All fighters, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} is now heading\N{\c&He1e1e1&}toward the large battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} is now heading\N{\c&He1e1e1&}toward the large battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commander, Spica Platoon,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}thank you for the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Matrix energy at maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commence intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Pressurize cylinder RPMs to maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Compression injector reading 2800!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Pressure valves half-open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Compression injector reading 2800!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Pressure valves half-open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Energy output at maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Rotate main guns!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Target the enemy ship! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Rotate main guns!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Target the enemy ship! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You miserable insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} is unarmed! Don't let\N{\c&He1e1e1&}them get a single shot on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So they've come, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can still fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You two go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I will watch over {\i1}Big One.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David, Manabu, get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is everyone... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We are all right. Everyone is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I sure botched that one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I sure botched that one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm fine. Hurry and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me take care of this.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I promise, I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me take care of this.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I promise, I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't make that face. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Want to bet on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sure. Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Manabu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am your absolute ruler.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Eliminate those useless beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Prepare to return fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There are more and more\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of them gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Treele. She's Leafle's sister.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}She saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You guys are different from the evil\N{\c&He1e1e1&}people we were told that you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We are the same as you.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We have souls, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where is Manabu... and everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That last attack hit the power reactor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Listen to what I have to say, Foresis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is no place for\N{\c&He1e1e1&}worms like you to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why are you after the Galaxy Railways!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do not come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Foresis-sama, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}These people are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Treele!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Galaxy Railways that you have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}extended throughout the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...and the space tracks that you have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}endlessly laid out, like nerve fibers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}they are beginning to create\N{\c&He1e1e1&}interference throughout our universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Galaxy... Railways are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Galaxy Railways must be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}by which our Master says the balance\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of the universe can be preserved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu... Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You'll be okay, Manabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Like I said, I won't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}let anyone take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm all right... Louis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've all been watching over it...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Father... Big Brother Mamoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce... my friends...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we've all been watching over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If there is another universe,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}then the Galaxy Railways will go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}forever connecting\N{\c&He1e1e1&}people's hearts and hopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It is the infinite bond that ties...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}all the lives in the universe together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Guardian of Fate, our Master,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is the one who presides over all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am the Envoy of Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You are not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Fate is something you should\N{\c&He1e1e1&}be able to change by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Fate is something you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}carve out for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why, you... Treele!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Foresis-sama...{\i0}
